{"tid":1038264,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"依加身處喺北九州嘅巴/絲打請入一入嚟","createTime":"2019-02-26T14:14:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-05T01:38:38.000Z","uid":105624,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"22125bba8c6679d2ec331a2831bf723e903c2653","tid":1038264,"uid":105624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T14:14:05.000Z","msg":"有無住/咁啱係日本旅行緊嘅巴打可以幫我一個忙?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n話說我尋日搭jr嗰時跌咗嘢，去到夜晚同今日朝早都話無，點知傍晚嗰時再去問，竟然話有人執到，搵得翻！&nbsp;(睇翻record其實原來尋晚已經執到，可能語言不通雞同鴨講唔明先話無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n宜加中央站嘅職員就比咗我樣失物嘅資料同埋個站嘅電話我，叫我打電話過去，同埋好似話可以將件失物send翻過嚟咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但係幣在我聽日就要翻嚟香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啱啱試下搵酒店幫手，佢都幫我打電話過去，但個職員話嗰面收咗工，要聽朝8點先開工，聽朝會試下再幫我打過去喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過我覺得酒店都幫唔到我，可能最終都係要去翻嗰個站拎/就算send翻嚟鹿兒島中央站我都拎唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以想問下有無巴絲打咁啱係九州住/讀緊書/旅行緊可以幫到我，起碼可以打電話過去叫佢幫我hold住樣嘢，唔好dom咗佢先，等我下次去旅行/有fd去都拎得翻嗎(好似話只會keep到呢個月28號)<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b87fac09c29cce0ea2cab7db74ae08db655bb863","tid":1038264,"uid":105624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T14:20:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"995c34c45e58a3cdf8fa85fc999efbf8c74a8802","tid":1038264,"uid":105624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T16:21:30.000Z","msg":"推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a870cc5b39148d726e22978c74adcf5b5ffb09c","tid":1038264,"uid":208722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T16:29:54.000Z","msg":"大分有別府地獄，下次去玩下再攞"},{"pid":"01d81f400cf9c7944ea3673fa5551ad4b64907a4","tid":1038264,"uid":105624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a870cc5b39148d726e22978c74adcf5b5ffb09c","tid":1038264,"uid":208722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T16:29:54.000Z","msg":"大分有別府地獄，下次去玩下再攞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T16:41:56.000Z","msg":"我都想呀，但佢話只會keep到28號，之後唔知佢會點處理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c87eaf55f837d1128ea0c1224bc244db43c0e9c","tid":1038264,"uid":105624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T08:55:18.000Z","msg":"今朝酒店幫我打咗去問，話無得幫我transfer翻嚟鹿兒島，要自己去大分站拎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  jr只會keep 2個禮拜，之後就會送去差館，差館就只會keep多3個月，跟住應該就會毀滅咗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n問過話有無得幫我extend，都係話要我自己去個站到搞，如果我去到就自己去埋拎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無巴打可以幫下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75f6992a3c4ee9d1725d5cb56b454fc2ed6b77b9","tid":1038264,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T09:45:34.000Z","msg":"大分冇咩遊客會特登去, 好重要既咪買張機票來回福岡再去大分拎囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce0712a61d6021308fb6d025c5bb31553a7bbb8b","tid":1038264,"uid":105624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T02:40:26.000Z","msg":"推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d73122b878f3c9b4bbf4c53a9d3efe6334efa1f","tid":1038264,"uid":38440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T03:42:39.000Z","msg":"件野重唔重要？btw你幾點機"},{"pid":"fcb4c09fa794d535d059a32712f43d3e8a4a85dd","tid":1038264,"uid":6239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T04:21:39.000Z","msg":"藍芽耳機就算鳩數啦，又要麻煩到人幫你去大分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1add2ee719abac8b